1. *Postane* li on čovekom, ne znamo. (Will he become a man, we don't know.)
2. *Postane* li srećan, to je na njemu. (Whether he becomes happy, it's up to him.)
3. On će za kratko vreme *postati* čovekom. (He will become a man shortly.)
4. On će *postati* uspešan čovek. (He will become a successful man.)
5. On će jednog dana *postati* mudar. (He will become wise one day.)